      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">For a full side-by-side comparison of iTalki and Preply, see our <a href="/compare/italki-vs-preply/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">iTalki vs Preply comparison</a>.</p>


