          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Is iTalki cheaper than Preply?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">iTalki tends to be slightly cheaper for community tutors, starting at $3/hour compared to Preply's minimum of around $10/hour. However, professional teachers on both platforms charge similar rates.</p>
